Package civitas.celestis.math.tuple

Class Pair<E>

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.math.tuple.Pair<E>
Type Parameters:
E - The type of element to contain in this pair
All Implemented Interfaces:
Tuple<E>, Serializable, Iterable<E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
UnorderedPair
public class Pair<E> extends Object implements Tuple<E>
A shallowly immutable pair of elements. Pairs are considered equal when both the order and composition are equal.
